INSERT INTO company (id, "createdAt", name, description, phone, email, website, location, type, image, slug) VALUES (178, '2020-09-10 19:46:56.518551+00', 'Oda', 'We do online grocery right. 

The company was founded in 2013 by 10 entrepreneurs with the goal of making Norway''s best shopping experience for groceries and making everyday life easier for Norway''s diverse population. 

[Oda](https://oda.com) focus on innovative and inspiring usability and streamlined logistics, offering both pick-up and delivery. Our selection is full and growing, and our prices are fair. Our vision is to improve people''s everyday lives through saving time and making smart choices simple. Now, [Oda](https://oda.com) is one of the fastest growing companies in the Nordic region. 

We use technology to create the grocery experience of the future, building our entire digital platform from scratch.With most of the entire tech world chasing to increase the time their users spend with their products, we optimise for the opposite; minimal time spent. In fact, we [save our customers 60+ hours in stores each year](https://www.aftenposten.no/brandstudio/feature/v/kolonial/tidsundersøkelsen/). And that’s even before we have fully personalised our user experience. Our efficient logistics save tons of food waste, and each new electric vehicle we add to our optimised distribution network [replaces 12.775 trips to the store each year](https://kommunikasjon.ntb.no/pressemelding/kolonialno-er-forst-ute-med-a-levere-matvarer-i-elbil?publisherId=12583954&releaseId=17860592). 

We believe that both customers and our society are ready for a brand new retail infrastructure. If [software is eating the world](https://a16z.com/2011/08/20/why-software-is-eating-the-world), we are creating the software that makes this new retail infrastructure possible — fueled by data and great UX.', NULL, NULL, 'https://oda.com', NULL, 'UNKNOWN', 'https://github.com/image/908', 'Oda_178');

